title: #26 Heated Transgender vs Lesbian Debate
description:
This week we host a very long, very heated debate between noted Transgender activist, JJ Marie Gufreda and AConservativeLesbian.com's Cynthia Yockey. Is transgenderism the "new normal"? Listen to find out.
Also, special appearances by Stalker Jim and Jordan Crowder!
